title: Nine’s Contract Public Enemy Number91 - Novel Updates
author: Nikaidou Hiroshi   二階堂 紘嗣
description: Ichijuki’s detective agency. A single shield put up at a shabby building. There, the silver-haired girl Ichikuji and the man in black Ninomae made themselves at home. Bound to a contract, a single wish if you will, they’re hunting souls. They are demons, waiting for the next human to come knocking on the rusty door of their agency.>
